reviewText: G​reat to get an overall idea of what Marketing Analytics is about
I learn how to do marketing planning, experiment, and analyze conversion.
Well designed course. Loved the instructor’s approach. Broke down complex concepts into easily understood bits.
Amazing, i wish there was a data set so i can practive on Tableau however.
I feel that this course has given me many tools to be able to apply them to marketing from an analytics perspective. This course has taught me to recognize the consumer perspective and their journey.
Muy buen curso, te explica todo a detalle y es muy facil de comprenderlo y ponerlo a prueba.
S​o much tools to analyze where do you spend your budget for marketing and as well great for decision making when allocating resources to increase profits ans decrease expenses.
It was one of the best courses I ever had, the instructor was very knowledgeable and methodic.
